creator: Wisdom Capital
descriptionHtml:
Wisdom Neo is one of the most advanced mobile trading apps available for beginner to advanced level of traders. Introduced by Wisdom Capital, a leading discount broker in Indian share market.
The Wisdom Neo is enabled with all the features of a versatile trading platform summarized within the app.
Offered with the most competitive zero brokerage plans and the highest leverage up to 60 times in the market.
Wisdom Neo is featured with the fastest trade execution and an extensive array of scanner facilities and chart displays.
Zero Brokerage charges in NSE in all Segments including Equity, Future & Options and MCX in Freedom Plan.
Flat Rs. 9/-trade in F&O and MCX in NSE under advanced trading plans other than the freedom plan.

The distinct features of the Wisdom Neo trading apps include:-

•Zero brokerage charges in NSE across all segments.

•View of Real Market Movements

•Top movers (Top gainers , Top losers, Top values).

•Order history, Trades and Net Positions

•Position Holding

•Share trading app designed to offer top speed even on the lowest bandwidth.

•Support of NSE and MCX exchanges and segments (Equity, F&O, Currency, Commodity).

•More than nine chart types including Bar, Candle, Colored Bar, Hollow Candle, Line, Mountain, Volume, Candle, Heikin-Ashi and Aagi.

•Around 100 indicators to analyze charts to make a well informed decision is available in Wisdom Capital online trading app.

•Instant trade placement and order book update without any glitches.

•Available in both dark as well as bright mode.

•Offering all product types including CNC, MIS, NRML, BO and CO, SIMPLE and AMO.

•Order types- Limit Order, Market Order, Stop Loss, Stop Loss-Market Order.

•The file size of Wisdom Neo app is the lowest in the Indian stock market 3 MB before installation.
